text: Ogie Henry Banks III (born June 13, 1973) is an American voice actor. He is best known for his roles as Clawd Wolf in Monster High and Luke Cage and Miles Morales in Ultimate Spider-Man. He also voices Dylan in the Bratz franchise and Darui in Naruto. ==Other websites== Category:Living people Category:1973 births Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles
